持民主 但乜柒都唔做<br />\n<br />\n你係咪會去批鬥下佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T23:40:37.000Z","msg":"唔係話批鬥人呀<br />\n但係你自己諗下<br />\n可能佢咁啱佢個friend 圈子或者屋企人係黃所以佢先係黃<br />\n 完全冇自己了解過或者有自己思想<br />\n我識有一個朋友 佢之前返香港有推鐵馬<br />\n但係佢反問返我14年嗰陣係咪因為23條出嚟<br />\n嗰刻我喺度諗其實有啲人真係唔係好了解<br />\n為出而出 人云亦云"},{"pid":"64504090eec202c139613198955cfb05d00e8976","tid":2009370,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"離地撚<br />\n不過點解要咩人都分黃藍"},{"pid":"bb6f0280ce2dc1fe3c999d77d020380a03343a7d","tid":2009370,"uid":205043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T00:11:03.000Z","msg":"憎人富貴厭人窮大會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a40004c4e2efeb19fea21684f9151190a80fb7","tid":2009370,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f09ca5c72267e4a1f062cdd5e2ba10ce2bb8945","tid":2009370,"uid":9104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:53:15.000Z","msg":"識幾個 對成件事少講 少接觸 覺得用磚頭好暴力 uncivilized囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:13:00.000Z","msg":"civilized就係用槍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c610ad6c4208aa65ba6e02489ed3f6c747d8bcbf","tid":2009370,"uid":146805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8ad0b731976114b6e900a1d7381b339fa8e02ef","tid":2009370,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"唔係香港出世長大，係咪唔會對香港呢個地方有感情？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"點會黃？<br />\n唔諗下佢地老豆老母都係香港<br />\n點解佢地仔女同普通香港人唔同<br />\n有得係外國出世/讀書？<br />\n因為人地老豆老母剝削下面既香港人<br />\n先有多餘錢support<br />\n係咁既環境長大<br />\n自然認同天生佢班竹星就係剝削他人既存在<br />\n黎為自己獲利<br />\n咁又點會黃？"},{"pid":"e6c964d40f5369d21a0e1d2071f8fcaedb65f2a4","tid":2009370,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"767483d97d0e73a91933da679e6da3a18258